Package: tidytrials
Title: Query and Tidy ClinicalTrials.gov Data in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Peter", "Nguyen", email = "phan.nguyen@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an R interface to the ClinicalTrials.gov v2 API with
    keyword search, advanced filtering, and automatic pagination. Returns
    raw study records and metadata to support reproducible data extraction.
